T1  - Asprosin in health and disease, a new glucose sensor with central and peripheral metabolic effects.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.3389/fendo.2022.1101091
A1  - Farrag, Mariam
A1  - Ait Eldjoudi, Djedjiga
A1  - Gonzalez-Rodriguez, Maria
A1  - Cordero-Barreal, Alfonso
A1  - Ruiz-Fernandez, Clara
