T1  - Pancreatic fat relates to fasting insulin and postprandial lipids but not polycystic ovary syndrome in adolescents with obesity.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1002/oby.23317
A1  - Ware, Meredith A
A1  - Kaar, Jill L
A1  - Diniz Behn, Cecilia
A1  - Bartlette, Kai
A1  - Carreau, Anne-Marie
A1  - Lopez-Paniagua, Dan
