T1  - Nutritional guidelines for the management of insulin resistance.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1080/10408398.2021.1908223
A1  - Muscogiuri, Giovanna
A1  - Barrea, Luigi
A1  - Caprio, Massimiliano
A1  - Ceriani, Florencia
A1  - Chavez, Alberto O
A1  - El Ghoch, Marwan
A1  - Frias-Toral, Evelyn
A1  - Mehta, Rucha J
