T1  - Licogliflozin versus placebo in women with polycystic ovary syndrome: A randomized, double-blind, phase 2 trial.
T3  - Comment in: Nat Rev Endocrinol. 2021 Oct;17(10):577 PMID: 34316043 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/34316043]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1111/dom.14495
A1  - Tan, Susanne
A1  - Ignatenko, Stanislav
A1  - Wagner, Frank
A1  - Dokras, Anuja
A1  - Seufert, Jochen
A1  - Zwanziger, Denise
A1  - Dunschen, Karin
A1  - Zakaria, Marjorie
A1  - Huseinovic, Neda
