T1  - Probiotic supplementation and the effects on weight loss, glycaemia and lipid profiles in women with polycystic ovary syndrome: a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled trial.
T3  - Expression of Concern in: Hum Fertil (Camb). 2021 Dec;24(5):395. doi: 10.1080/14647273.2020.1841980 PMID: 33143448 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/33143448] Update in: Hum Fertil (Camb). 2021 Dec;24(5):395. doi: 10.1080/14647273.2020.1841980 PMID: 33143448 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/33143448] Retraction in: Hum Fertil (Camb). 2024 Dec;27(1):2373595. doi: 10.1080/14647273.2024.2373595 PMID: 38953512 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/38953512]
