T1  - An International Consortium Update: Pathophysiology, Diagnosis, and Treatment of Polycystic Ovarian Syndrome in Adolescence.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1159/000479371
A1  - Ibanez, Lourdes
A1  - Oberfield, Sharon E
A1  - Witchel, Selma
A1  - Auchus, Richard J
A1  - Chang, R Jeffrey
A1  - Codner, Ethel
